    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult female holotype dorsum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718095>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult female paratype dorsum. A—photographed using differential interference contrast (DIC), and B—phase contrast." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718097>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult female holotype venter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718099>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult female legs I–IV (right side; legs I–III dorsal aspect, leg IV abaxial aspect); with detail of ventral aspect tarsi I–III, and adaxial aspect tarsus IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718099/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718103>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult male. A—dorsum; B—detail of palp (dorsal and ventral aspect) and basal insertion of solenidion." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718103/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718105>
    dc:description "FIGURE 45. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., adult male. A— posterior venter; B—detail of aedeagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718107>
    dc:description "FIGURE 46. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov. adult male legs I and III (right side, dorsal to adaxial aspect), with detail of abaxial aspect of tarsi (n. b., the seta * on femur I is an asymmetrical aberration)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10718109>
    dc:description "FIGURE 48. Extenuipalpus situngu sp. nov., deutonymph legs I–IV (right side, dorsal aspect); with detail of ventral aspect all tarsi, and left tarsus I (dorsal and ventral aspects) (n. b. several setae are missing: ft′ is missing on both tarsi I, l″ is missing on genu I and tibiae I–II; and ft′ illustrated separately on tarsi III–IV)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10718109/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

